Yes the airdrops will be distributed to holders of XRP so what does it matter of the XRP lawsuit?  Regardless of the outcome (whenever that may be) FLR / SGB will still be airdropped to the eligible XRP holders.

Songbird and Flare are completely separate networks from the XRPL.  Yes, the airdrops were based on the amount of XRP held in wallets but that does not influence (in any way what so ever) the legal status of $FLR / $SGB as assets.
